You can simply ask Alexa to turn your AQiA smart products on and off through voice command. You can also ask Alexa to dim your smart bulbs, change their color, etc.

To get started, connect your AQiA app account with Alexa:
1. Download our “AQiA” app in app market, then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
2. Configure our devices in “AQiA” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable “AQiA” skill on Alexa app, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say “Search complete”;
5. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to green.”
